{
  "stem": "7414.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we did not really know much of the tension between till the two, three years before the war when the pressure of the anti-Semitism, which came from Germany on a-- somehow it did.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was so strong that you could-- you-- you could see the pickets in front of the Jewish shops.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Don't buy from the Jews or something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when we started really to feel the government pressure on fiscal and economic on the Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But till-- till then, it was quite peaceful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had, for example, as a Jewish community of 20-odd thousand people, we had our own institution.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had our own council, which was called Kahal, with our president.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we had our schools.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had our hospital, Jewish hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had our bath house, yes, and of course, all the synagogues.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And one of the oldest in Poland-- a beautiful synagogue-- was just opposite us where we lived at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to primary school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after the-- those two incidents, which hurt me, everything went quiet, and not-- not only quiet, but the teacher who's tried to divide us in the beginning was very friendly with us because we-- because we were mostly the good pupils, you know, the Jewish kids.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother went to business, the oldest one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But from Rosa down, we were all excellent in schools-- school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rosa, for example, was a special-- her special subjects were mathematics and physics.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my brother, the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my inclination was towards languages, history, and things like this, rather humanistic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were all very good at school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It means we finished ever year with distinctions and our matriculation was with distinction.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the problem started when my sister Rosa wanted to go to university.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
